The eligible expenditure covered by the financial contribution from the Community
1. The financial contribution from the Community as referred to in Article 1 shall only be made in respect of justified and reasonable payments for the eligible costs as set out in Annex I.
2. The financial contribution from the Community as referred to in Article 1 shall exclude:
(a) value added tax;
(b) salaries of civil servants;
(c) use of public material other than consumables.
